♪You stand guard alone outside the door♪

00:42:07.140 --> 00:42:09.810
♪The obsession held within is sharp♪

00:42:10.100 --> 00:42:12.920
♪It cuts through everything,
leaving no way back♪

00:42:14.160 --> 00:42:16.770
♪Cobwebs are woven into a net♪

00:42:16.770 --> 00:42:19.410
♪Each strand is a lead♪

00:42:21.120 --> 00:42:26.000
♪Fate hangs above your head
like a suspended blade♪

00:42:28.140 --> 00:42:30.740
♪You swallow so much frustration♪

00:42:30.910 --> 00:42:33.330
♪And push the door open
with your own hands♪

00:42:35.090 --> 00:42:37.620
♪What's meant to come will always come♪

00:42:37.920 --> 00:42:40.810
♪You stop the pendulum of hesitation♪

00:42:42.020 --> 00:42:44.640
♪Only when darkness admits it is dark♪

00:42:44.640 --> 00:42:47.360
♪Can innocence return to the light♪

00:42:48.920 --> 00:42:51.580
♪The curtain of the truth
is drawn aside♪

00:42:51.580 --> 00:42:55.820
♪You cross through pain
to reach the other shore♪

00:42:55.940 --> 00:42:59.280
♪You demand tears to come crashing down♪

00:42:59.440 --> 00:43:02.840
♪You demand old dreams
to grow into rainbows♪

00:43:02.840 --> 00:43:06.270
♪You demand dust
to stir up raging waves♪

00:43:06.380 --> 00:43:09.880
♪Souls will rise again♪

00:43:09.880 --> 00:43:13.230
♪You demand fate
turn generous from now on♪

00:43:13.360 --> 00:43:16.780
♪To return everything
it once took from you♪

00:43:16.780 --> 00:43:19.420
♪You demand tomorrow♪

00:43:19.420 --> 00:43:22.460
♪To bloom beyond the ruins♪

00:43:22.460 --> 00:43:24.150
♪The light will come♪

