♪Who keeps warmth alive♪

00:43:40.460 --> 00:43:43.330
♪And beholds
flowers bloom in the abyss?♪

00:43:43.500 --> 00:43:47.200
♪Who never stops calling out♪

00:43:47.200 --> 00:43:50.590
♪And finally opens their eyes♪

00:43:50.700 --> 00:43:53.650
♪From a long slumber?♪

00:43:53.760 --> 00:43:55.100
♪The light will come♪

00:43:55.100 --> 00:43:58.400
♪You demand to pass through
life's perils in peace♪

00:43:58.580 --> 00:44:01.960
♪You demand to decide your own fate♪

00:44:01.960 --> 00:44:04.610
♪You demand the future♪

00:44:04.610 --> 00:44:07.670
♪To flourish right before your eyes♪

